commit.message: Add new runscript for extended statistics collection
Added some instrumentation for measuring terms and cached rewriting
Added option to print all built-in strategies.
Provided access to built-in strategies via --print-strategy
Fixed clause collection bug (for true literals), version number
Fixed wrong handling of negations for trivial literals
Some minor updates to the manual, version number
Simplified parsed string handling with PermaStings
Fixed more bugs exposed by higher-order answer generation
Some cleanup, fixed memory leak and performance bug (wrong handling of heuristics in auto mode)
Minor updates of docs after 3.0 announcement
Removen non-optimisation optimisation of questionable correctness for HO
